WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: sq

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
Translator: Iris Xholi
Reviewer: Helena Bedalli

00:00:12.906 --> 00:00:23.303
Hetain Patel: (Ne Kinezce)

00:00:23.303 --> 00:00:26.606
Yuyu Tau: Pershendetje, une jam Hetain. Jam artist.

00:00:26.606 --> 00:00:28.467
Dhe kjo eshte Yuyu.

00:00:28.467 --> 00:00:30.886
Ajo eshte nje kercimtare me te cilen punoj.

00:00:30.886 --> 00:00:34.492
I kam kerkuar te perktheje per mua.

00:00:34.492 --> 00:00:39.182
HP: (Ne Kinezce)

00:00:39.182 --> 00:00:41.890
YR: Nese mundem, do te me pelqente te tregoja

00:00:41.890 --> 00:00:43.620
pak per veten

00:00:43.620 --> 00:00:45.916
dhe artin tim.

00:00:45.916 --> 00:00:51.459
HP: (Ne Kinezce)

00:00:51.459 --> 00:00:54.583
YR: Kam lindur e jam rritur prane Manchester,

00:00:54.583 --> 00:00:55.550
ne Angli,

00:00:55.550 --> 00:00:59.122
por nuk kam per t'jua thene ne anglisht,

00:00:59.122 --> 00:01:01.883
sepse po perpiqem te shmang ndonje supozim

00:01:01.883 --> 00:01:04.965
qe mund te behen nga theksi im verior.

00:01:04.965 --> 00:01:07.540
(Te Qeshura)

00:01:07.540 --> 00:01:16.975
HP: (Ne Kinezce)

00:01:16.975 --> 00:01:19.487
YR: Problemi i vetem ishte qe ta maskoja

00:01:19.487 --> 00:01:21.037
me Kinezce Mandarin

00:01:21.037 --> 00:01:23.755
eshte qe di te them vec kete paragraf,

00:01:23.755 --> 00:01:25.534
te cilin e kam mesuar permendesh

00:01:25.534 --> 00:01:28.204
kur isha per vizite ne Kine. (Te qeshura)

00:01:28.204 --> 00:01:32.092
Pra, e vetmja c'ka mund te bej eshte ti perserisja me tone te ndryshme

00:01:32.092 --> 00:01:33.952
dhe shpresoj qe mos kuptohej.

00:01:33.952 --> 00:01:39.301
(Te qeshura)

00:01:39.301 --> 00:01:43.481
HP: (Ne Kinezce)

00:01:43.481 --> 00:01:44.848
(Te qeshura)

00:01:44.848 --> 00:01:47.961
YR: E panevojshme te them qe i kerkoj ndjese

00:01:47.961 --> 00:01:52.444
ndonje folesi te Mandarin ne audience.

00:01:54.214 --> 00:01:56.887
Kur femije, do ta urreja kur me detyronin

00:01:56.887 --> 00:01:59.515
te vishja nje pizhame kurta indiane,

00:01:59.515 --> 00:02:02.513
sepse nuk mendoja se ish i lezetshem.

00:02:02.513 --> 00:02:05.814
Me dukej pak si vajzeror, si nje fustan,

00:02:05.814 --> 00:02:08.472
dhe e kish kete pjese paksa te fryre

00:02:08.472 --> 00:02:10.715
te cilen duhej ta lidhje vertete fort

00:02:10.715 --> 00:02:14.139
qe te shmangie sikletin e te renit.

00:02:14.139 --> 00:02:16.175
Babai im nuk e veshi me,

00:02:16.175 --> 00:02:19.100
kshq nuk e shihja te arsyeshme ta vishja as une.

00:02:19.100 --> 00:02:22.453
Gjithashtu, me ben te ndjehem pak ne siklet,

00:02:22.453 --> 00:02:25.148
kur njerezit mendojne se paraqes dicka

00:02:25.148 --> 00:02:27.474
me te vertete Indiane kur e vesh,

00:02:27.474 --> 00:02:30.923
sepse nuk eshte ashtu si ndjehem.

00:02:30.923 --> 00:02:36.775
HP: (Ne Kinezce)

00:02:36.775 --> 00:02:39.702
YR: Faktikisht, e vetmja menyre qe me ben te ndjehem rehat

00:02:39.702 --> 00:02:42.110
ti vesh ato eshte te shtirem

00:02:42.110 --> 00:02:45.321
sikur ato jane rrobat e nje luftetari kung fu-je

00:02:45.321 --> 00:02:48.060
si Li Mu Bai nga ai filmi,

00:02:48.060 --> 00:02:52.373
"Tiger i perkulshem, Dragua i fshehur."

00:02:52.373 --> 00:02:57.556
(Muzike)

00:03:35.383 --> 00:03:36.992
OK.

00:03:36.992 --> 00:03:44.063
Pra, arti im eshte rreth identitetit dhe gjuhes,

00:03:44.063 --> 00:03:46.793
duke sfiduar supozime te rrenjosura

00:03:46.793 --> 00:03:51.338
bazuar ne pamjen qe kemi ose origjinen tone,

00:03:51.338 --> 00:03:55.082
si gjinia, raca, klasa sociale.

00:03:55.082 --> 00:03:58.933
Kush na ben ne ata qe jemi?

00:03:58.933 --> 00:04:04.880
HP: (Ne Kinezce)

00:04:04.880 --> 00:04:07.256
YR: Dikur lexoja librat komik te Njeriut Merimange,

00:04:07.256 --> 00:04:08.831
shihja filma me Kung Fu,

00:04:08.831 --> 00:04:11.616
dhe merrja mesime filozofie nga Bruce Lee.

00:04:11.616 --> 00:04:13.265
Ai do te thoshte--

00:04:13.265 --> 00:04:15.352
HP: Zbraze mendjen tende.

00:04:15.352 --> 00:04:16.416
(Te qeshura)

00:04:16.416 --> 00:04:22.429
Ji pa forme, pa konture, si uji.

00:04:22.429 --> 00:04:24.419
Tani, mbushe nje gote me uje.

00:04:24.419 --> 00:04:27.315
Uji behet gota.

00:04:27.315 --> 00:04:30.422
Hedh uje ne nje shishe dhe uji behet shishja.

00:04:30.422 --> 00:04:33.801
Hidhe ne nje cajnik e behet cajniku.

00:04:33.801 --> 00:04:36.450
Pra, uji mund te rrjedhe

00:04:36.450 --> 00:04:39.100
ose mund te perplaset.

00:04:39.100 --> 00:04:42.455
Jini si uji, miqte e mi. (Duartrokitje)

00:04:42.455 --> 00:04:46.557
YR: Kete vit, mbush 32 vjec,

00:04:46.557 --> 00:04:49.676
kaq vjec ishte edhe Bruce Lee kur nderroi jete.

00:04:49.676 --> 00:04:52.270
Kohet e fudnit kam vrare mendjen,

00:04:52.270 --> 00:04:54.200
se cfare keshille do te me jepte sot

00:04:54.200 --> 00:04:56.226
rreth ketij fjalimi TED

00:04:56.226 --> 00:05:00.170
po te ish ende gjalle.

00:05:00.170 --> 00:05:03.908
HP: Mos e imito zerin tim.

00:05:03.908 --> 00:05:05.979
Me ofendon.

00:05:05.979 --> 00:05:08.009
(Te qeshura)

00:05:08.009 --> 00:05:09.760
YR: Keshille e mire,

00:05:09.760 --> 00:05:13.472
por une vazhdoj te jem i mendimit se ne mesojme kush jemi

00:05:13.472 --> 00:05:15.575
duke kopjuar te tjeret.

00:05:15.575 --> 00:05:19.792
Kush nga ju ne salle nuk e ka imituar heroin e tyre te vegjelise

00:05:19.792 --> 00:05:23.687
ne kendin e lojerave, ose mami e babin?

00:05:23.687 --> 00:05:25.948
Une e kam bere.

00:05:25.948 --> 00:05:30.490
HP: Disa vite te shkuara, ne menyre qe ta beja kete video

00:05:30.490 --> 00:05:34.495
per artin tim, une rruajta floket

00:05:34.495 --> 00:05:37.638
ne menyre qe ti rrisja si te babait tim

00:05:37.638 --> 00:05:40.404
kur emigroi per here te pare nga India

00:05:40.404 --> 00:05:43.668
ne UK, ne 1960-en.

00:05:43.668 --> 00:05:47.798
Ai i kish te ndara anash dhe mbante mustaqe.

00:05:47.798 --> 00:05:50.417
Ne fillim, gjithcka shkonte mire.

00:05:50.417 --> 00:05:53.467
Fillova te marr edhe ulje cmimi ne dyqanet indiane.

00:05:53.467 --> 00:05:57.468
(Te qeshura)

00:05:57.468 --> 00:05:59.092
Por me pas, shume shpejt,

00:05:59.092 --> 00:06:00.839
fillova te mos e vleresoja shume

00:06:00.839 --> 00:06:02.519
faktin qe mustaqja ime rritej shume,

00:06:02.519 --> 00:06:05.921
dhe u be shume e gjate.

00:06:05.921 --> 00:06:08.668
Nuk dukej me mustaqe indiane.

00:06:08.668 --> 00:06:10.511
Sakaq, njerezit nga trotuari tjeter,

00:06:10.511 --> 00:06:12.402
do te bertisnin me sa kishin ne koke--

00:06:12.402 --> 00:06:14.618
HP dhe YR: Arriba! Arriba! Andale! Andale!

00:06:14.618 --> 00:06:16.619
(Te qeshur)

00:06:16.619 --> 00:06:18.983
HP: Faktikisht, as nuk e di se pse po flas keshtu.

00:06:18.983 --> 00:06:21.987
Babi im nuk ka as theks indian tani.

00:06:21.987 --> 00:06:24.514
Ai flet keshtu tani.

00:06:24.514 --> 00:06:28.542
Pra, nuk eshte se kam imituar vetem babain.

00:06:28.542 --> 00:06:32.140
Disa vite me pare, shkova ne Kine per disa muaj,

00:06:32.140 --> 00:06:34.974
dhe nuk mund te flisja fare gjuhen Kineze,

00:06:34.974 --> 00:06:36.786
c'ka me nervozonte se tepermi,

00:06:36.786 --> 00:06:40.738
kshq e shkrova kete gje dhe e perktheva

00:06:40.738 --> 00:06:47.225
ne Kinezce dhe e mesova permendesh,

00:06:47.225 --> 00:06:50.422
sikunder bejme me muziken do thoja.

00:06:50.422 --> 00:06:53.763
YR:Kjo fjali eshte ngulitur tashme ne mendjen time

00:06:53.763 --> 00:06:56.642
me forte sesa kodi i bankes sime,

00:06:56.642 --> 00:07:00.570
ndaj mund te shtirem sikur e flas shkelqyeshem Kinezcen.

00:07:00.570 --> 00:07:02.618
Kur e mesova kete fjali,

00:07:02.618 --> 00:07:05.354
kisha nje artist ne krahe per te me degjuar

00:07:05.354 --> 00:07:07.823
se sa mire e artikuloja ate.

00:07:07.823 --> 00:07:10.309
E thashe fjaline e ai qeshi

00:07:10.309 --> 00:07:13.120
e me tha, "Oh, po shume mire,

00:07:13.120 --> 00:07:15.493
vetem se me tingellon pak si femer."

00:07:15.493 --> 00:07:16.955
I thashe, "Cfare?"

00:07:16.955 --> 00:07:20.877
Ai tha, "Po, ti ke mesuar nga nje grua?"

00:07:20.877 --> 00:07:22.881
I thashe, " Po. Edhe?"

00:07:22.881 --> 00:07:25.522
Me pas ai me shpjegoi diferencat dhe vecorite ne ton

00:07:25.522 --> 00:07:27.772
mes zerit mashkullor e atij femeror

00:07:27.772 --> 00:07:31.574
dhe qe une e kisha mesuar mire,

00:07:31.574 --> 00:07:33.567
por me nje ze femre.

00:07:33.567 --> 00:07:35.790
(Te qeshura)

00:07:35.790 --> 00:07:43.100
(Duartrokitje)

00:07:43.100 --> 00:07:46.519
HP: OK. Atehere, ky biznesi i imitimeve

00:07:46.519 --> 00:07:48.204
i paska rreziqet e veta.

00:07:48.204 --> 00:07:50.912
Nuk shkon gjithmone sipas planit,

00:07:50.912 --> 00:07:54.382
edhe me nje perkthyes te talentuar.

00:07:54.382 --> 00:07:56.668
Por do ti qendroj kesaj,

00:07:56.668 --> 00:08:01.033
sepse ne kundershtim me ate qe mund te hamendesojme,

00:08:01.033 --> 00:08:05.132
te imituarit e dikujt mund te nxjerre ne pah dicka unike.

00:08:05.132 --> 00:08:08.387
Pra, sa here deshtoja

00:08:08.387 --> 00:08:10.943
te isha si babai im,

00:08:10.943 --> 00:08:14.838
behesha me shume vetvetja.

00:08:14.838 --> 00:08:19.420
Sa here qe deshtoja te isha Bruce Lee,

00:08:19.420 --> 00:08:23.066
behesha me autentik.

00:08:23.066 --> 00:08:24.551
Ky eshte arti im.

00:08:24.551 --> 00:08:27.871
Une kerkoj gjithnje origjinalitet,

00:08:27.871 --> 00:08:30.106
edhe neqoftese ky i fundit vjen ne nje forme

00:08:30.106 --> 00:08:33.802
qe nuk para pritet.

00:08:33.802 --> 00:08:38.038
Eshte vetem kohet e fundit qe kam filluar te kuptoj

00:08:38.038 --> 00:08:41.745
qe nuk e kam mesuar te qendruarit ulur keshtu

00:08:41.745 --> 00:08:43.891
ngaqe jam Indian.

00:08:43.891 --> 00:08:47.167
Kete e mesova nga Njeriu Merimange.

00:08:47.167 --> 00:08:48.905
(Te qeshura)

00:08:48.905 --> 00:08:50.462
Faleminderit.

00:08:50.462 --> 00:08:56.478
(Duartrokitje)

